title: Taking you Down to Chinatown
itunes:title: Taking you Down to Chinatown
description:
Anthony, Gregg and Erica reflect on their dinner out in china town and Anthony had to get a janitor to unlock the studio door for him. A woman ate her diamond engagement ring in her sleep and an 80 year old sportscaster was fired over some racist remarks.
This episode is brought to you by The Lead, a podcast by Wondery and The Athletic.
